---

# Transit API Documentation

## 1. Standard Response Format

### Success Response

* Body

```
{
  "success": true,
  "data": {},
  "error": null
}
```

### Error Response

* Body

```
{
  "success": false,
  "data": null,
  "error": {
    "code": "ERROR_CODE",
    "message": "Error message"
  }
}
```

## 2. Date Format

All timestamps are ISO 8601 UTC strings.

Example:

```
"2026-02-17T03:21:45.123Z"
```

## 3. Coordinate Format

```
{ "lat": number, "lng": number }
```

## 4. GET /v1/routes

* Response 200 (application/json)

```
{
  "success": true,
  "data": {
    "routes": [
      {
        "id": "271",
        "shortName": "271",
        "longName": "Bellevue College to U District",
        "color": "#3B82F6",
        "agencyName": "King County Metro"
      }
    ]
  },
  "error": null
}
```

## 5. GET /v1/routes/:id

* Response 200 (application/json)

```
{
  "success": true,
  "data": {
    "route": {
      "id": "271",
      "shortName": "271",
      "longName": "Bellevue College to U District",
      "color": "#3B82F6",
      "agencyName": "King County Metro",
      "polyline": "encoded_polyline_string",
      "stops": [
        {
          "name": "Bellevue College",
          "time": "3:24 PM",
          "tag": "Next stop"
        }
      ]
    }
  },
  "error": null
}
```

## 6. GET /v1/arrivals

* Response 200 (application/json)

```
{
  "success": true,
  "data": {
    "arrivals": [
      {
        "id": "271",
        "destination": "Seattle",
        "arrivalMin": 4,
        "confidence": 94,
        "status": "early"
      }
    ]
  },
  "error": null
}
```

## 7. GET /v1/predictions/delay

* Response 200 (application/json)

```
{
  "success": true,
  "data": {
    "prediction": {
      "routeId": "271",
      "predictedDelayMinutes": 5.0,
      "percentile90DelayMinutes": 8.0,
      "confidence": 80.0,
      "sampleSize": 50,
      "timeBin": "08:00-09:00",
      "dayType": "weekday"
    }
  },
  "error": null
}
```

## 8. GET /v1/predictions/crowding

* Response 200 (application/json)

```
{
  "success": true,
  "data": {
    "prediction": {
      "routeId": "271",
      "predictedLevel": 3.5,
      "percentile90Level": 5.0,
      "confidence": 75.0,
      "sampleSize": 40
    }
  },
  "error": null
}
```

## 9. Error Example

* Response 404 (application/json)

```
{
  "success": false,
  "data": null,
  "error": {
    "code": "ROUTE_NOT_FOUND",
    "message": "Route not found"
  }
}
```
